import Grid2 from "@mui/material/Grid2"
import Card from "@mui/material/Card"

function Input_post()
{

    return (
        <Grid2 container spacing={2}
            Columns={5}>
            <Grid2 size={3}>
                <Card>
                    asfsd
                </Card>
            </Grid2>
            <Grid2 size={3}>
                <Card>
                    asfsd
                </Card>
            </Grid2>
            <Grid2 size={3}>
                <Card>
                    asfsd
                </Card>
            </Grid2>
            <Grid2>
                <Card>
                    asfsd
                </Card>
            </Grid2>
        </Grid2>
    );
}

export default Input_post;
